Flow Control Statements:

      Java provides three types of control flow statements.

                           (i)Decision Making statements / Selection Statements
                                  (a) if statements 
                                  (b) switch statement
                            (ii) Loop statements /Iterative Statements
                                    (a)do while loop
                                    (b)while loop
                                    (c)for loop
                                    (d)for-each loop
                            (iii) Jump statements / Transfer Statements
                                     (a)break statement 
                                     (b)continue statement
                                     (c)try/catch/finally statement
                                     (d) Assert statement